{"tid":224683,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"批評完你鐘意嘅嘢 轉個頭又跟風","createTime":"2017-05-01T08:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T15:19:36.000Z","uid":53197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67f92662aaf62ce5da8a98063f9ee9a607ecc536","tid":224683,"uid":53197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"你地有冇d朋友成日批評你鐘意嘅嘢 但過多一排轉呔話自己都好鐘意？<br />\n又或者有樣野明明你鐘意/睇中在先 佢只係買得早過你 你買完之後佢就話返你跟風？<br />\n<br />\n我以前有個fd乜鳩都踩<br />\n以前明明話我學日文好毒 但轉個頭又跟我學<br />\n我鐘意睇神話故事 話鳩我迷信 但之後又比我發現佢跟我睇<br />\n有幾個袋我睇中先但未有錢買住 佢只係早過我小小買 之後就話我跟風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明淘寶一百蚊都已經買到好多嘢 佢話我淘寶好撚哂錢 但自己都成身名牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚反智<br />\n呢類人真係好討厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：已經疏遠呢位人類"},{"pid":"68886bcdfc8349cebb46e2e069f47ec8b2208323","tid":224683,"uid":53197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:59:29.000Z","msg":"鐘意同自己一樣嘅野唔緊要<br />\n但批評完先黎鐘意就好討厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514252616f457b709fc219587550d5d4c871fd74","tid":224683,"uid":65013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"上年未興cons之前買左對1970s 被人話我老土<br />\n而家興返佢同我講想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好厭惡呢類人"},{"pid":"2a2baf387608df79ca39cf7f8ff7e38061f78c1f","tid":224683,"uid":53197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年未興cons之前買左對1970s 被人話我老土<br />\n而家興返佢同我講想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好厭惡呢類人</blockquote><br />\n我都係 好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d4082788357057d0b4cac7e3ecb474fdac3504","tid":224683,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"9c932e2f9e035d3d3befbdca637d2f7df74